Author: Sabine Witek
Content: What’s the reason why you can’t do a mono cleanse with apples? That would be so much easier for me 🤣

Author: Lyndon Forrester
Content: -Sabine Witek while I have never heard MM recommended it, Dr John Pagano has had many eat cooked apples for 3 days to help with skin conditions so some people have benefited from it.  However, it lacks cluster sodium and doesn’t enough of a have a complete nutrient profile generally unless paired with cucumber and celery.  He does recommend if someone chooses to do a juice fast, to do that particular combination which is kind of like a mono cleanse.
